<li><a href="/wiki/Amnon_Ben-Tor" title="Amnon Ben-Tor">Amnon Ben-Tor</a>: winner of the <a href="/wiki/Israel_Prize" title="Israel Prize">Israel Prize</a> for archaeology (2019)<sup id="cite_ref-13" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-13">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Yoram_Bilu" title="Yoram Bilu">Yoram Bilu</a>: winner of the <a href="/wiki/Israel_Prize" title="Israel Prize">Israel Prize</a> for Sociology and Anthropology (2013)<sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>
