<li>Yosef Kaplan: winner of the <a href="/wiki/Israel_Prize" title="Israel Prize">Israel Prize</a> for the history of the Jewish people (2013)<sup id="cite_ref-28" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-28">&#91;28&#93;</a></sup></li>
