<li><a href="/wiki/Michael_A._Meyer" title="Michael A. Meyer">Michael A. Meyer</a>: winner of the National Jewish Book Award (1968, 1989, 1997); co-founder of the <a href="/wiki/Association_for_Jewish_Studies" title="Association for Jewish Studies">Association for Jewish Studies</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-34" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-34">&#91;34&#93;</a></sup></li>
